<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,1445,1974]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,457,1517,1542]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">
<typeStatus box="[199,308,1517,1542]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">Holotype</typeStatus>
description.
</emphasis>
Length 
<quantity box="[555,645,1517,1542]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.6" pageId="4" pageNumber="579" unit="mm" value="4.6">4.6 mm</quantity>
. Vertex of head red, pronotum blue-green, elytra brown with 
<number box="[1351,1365,1517,1542]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579" value="6.0">6</number>
(
<number box="[1383,1396,1518,1542]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579" value="3.0">3</number>
+ 
<number box="[1414,1427,1518,1542]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579" value="3.0">3</number>
) spots of yellow pubescence. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[493,557,1553,1578]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">Head</emphasis>
with frons red, glabrous, with sculpture characterized by large punctures. Clypeus flat, depressed, green, without transverse carina. Antennae serrate from fifth segment. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1210,1331,1589,1614]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">Pronotum</emphasis>
wider on the posterior half. Disc with transverse striae. Premarginal carinula not entire, up to almost half the length of pronotum, surrounded by sparse white setae. Marginal carinae joined before the base. Mentonniere with anterior margin rounded. Prosternal plate wide, with rounded apex. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[819,938,1697,1722]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">Scutellum</emphasis>
transversely carinate. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1192,1308,1697,1722]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">Abdomen</emphasis>
with white pubescence on lateroterga, metepisterna and metacoxae. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[784,840,1733,1758]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579">Legs</emphasis>
metallic green. All claws simply toothed. Metatarsus shorter than metatibia. Basal metatarsomere shorter than the sum of the following two (
<number box="[1131,1141,1770,1794]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579" value="1.0">1</number>
&lt;
<number box="[1159,1175,1770,1794]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579" value="2.0">2</number>
+ 
<number box="[1193,1207,1770,1794]" pageId="4" pageNumber="579" value="3.0">3</number>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
